<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MediaLab Portfolio Template</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(34,211,238,0.18), transparent 30%), linear-gradient(155deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e0f2fe 48%, #eef2ff 100%); font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;">
    <div id="portfolio-hero" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 54px; top: 42px; width: min(1100px, calc(100vw - 108px)); height: 360px; border-radius: 38px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 40px 120px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.16);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 44px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 28px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #082f49 0%, #0f766e 42%, #155e75 100%); color: #ecfeff;">
        <div style="max-width: 58%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
          <div>
            <div style="display: inline-flex; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;">Creative Portfolio</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 22px 0 12px; font-size: 56px; line-height: 0.94; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">Alex Rowe builds elegant digital products.</h1>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(236,254,255,0.88);">A clean personal brand site for a designer, developer, or product lead. Showcase standout work, trusted partners, and a clear path to book your next project.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;">
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 18px; background: #ecfeff; color: #0f172a; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;">View Projects</a>
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(236,254,255,0.34); color: #ecfeff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;">Book a Call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="width: 300px; border-radius: 30px; padding: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
          <div style="width: 92px; height: 92px; border-radius: 28px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc 0%, #bae6fd 100%); color: #082f49; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800;">AR</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.16em; color: rgba(236,254,255,0.7);">This Month</div>
            <div style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800;">12 launches</div>
            <div style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(236,254,255,0.8);">Trusted by founders who want a high-converting, editorial-style landing page with strong personality.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div id="portfolio-work" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 54px; top: 434px; width: min(1100px, calc(100vw - 108px)); height: 290px; border-radius: 34px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 34px; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); display: flex; gap: 18px;">
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 28px; padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(155deg, #0f172a 0%, #1d4ed8 100%); color: #e0f2fe;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.7;">Case Study</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 16px 0 10px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.02;">Flux Payments</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; opacity: 0.88;">A fintech redesign with calmer onboarding, sharper trust signals, and a premium motion-led dashboard.</p>
          <div style="display: inline-flex; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Conversion +42%</div>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 28px; padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(160deg, #ecfeff 0%, #dbeafe 100%); color: #0f172a;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #0369a1;">Studio Offer</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 16px 0 10px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.02;">Portfolio Systems</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; color: #334155;">A ready-to-customize structure for experts who want a modern portfolio with proof, process, and premium contact flow.</p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <span style="padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: #ffffff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Case studies</span>
            <span style="padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: #ffffff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Services</span>
            <span style="padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: #ffffff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Booking CTA</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div id="portfolio-contact" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 54px; top: 756px; width: min(1100px, calc(100vw - 108px)); height: 210px; border-radius: 32px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.14);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 32px 36px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 26px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0fdfa 100%);">
        <div style="max-width: 62%;">
          <div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #0f766e;">Start a project</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 12px 0 10px; font-size: 38px; line-height: 1.02; color: #0f172a;">Turn your portfolio into a polished client magnet.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #475569;">Swap in your real work, tighten your offer, and publish a personal site that feels thoughtful on both laptop and phone.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 190px; padding: 16px 22px; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0891b2 0%, #0f766e 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800;">Contact Alex</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
